{"tid":455709,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)宇宙威龍 撕裂地平線 第五元素 星際特工","createTime":"2017-11-02T10:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T18:20:26.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b26644579d7d002a0d0c8a25e320ceb9cd8ac024","tid":455709,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=iqrmZALveYtknozCzSJN2aS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=63b6e863\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> V台入佢主頁睇先比較順<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=iqrmZALveYtknozCzSJN2aS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=f589a5fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/87/1990-Total-recall-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F87%2F1990-Total-recall-poster.jpg&h=a4715ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/8c/Event_horizon_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F8c%2FEvent_horizon_ver1.jpg&h=368d580f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/65/Fifth_element_poster_%281997%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F65%2FFifth_element_poster_%25281997%2529.jpg&h=fb9201da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a8/Valerian_and_the_City_of_a_Thousand_Planets_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa8%2FValerian_and_the_City_of_a_Thousand_Planets_Poster.jpg&h=2f80be6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事發生在2084年。Douglas Quaid是一個建築工人，一次他在地鐵上看到一個Rekall公司的廣告，這個公司可以把內存植入人腦，使人可以虛擬冒險，所以他決定購買一個在火星上的虛擬歷險，在這個歷險中他會扮演一個間諜。Quaid的同事告訴他Rekall具有風險，植入手術失敗可能造成類似腦白質切除術的後果，受害者會受到永久性的精神傷害。Quaid猶豫了一陣，但是卻忽視了這個警告。<br />\n<br />\n2.西元2040年，政府秘密製造的「Event Horizon號」太空船，要以新研發的重力驅動系統，製造出人造黑洞以進行時空重疊，可瞬間跳躍至數光年甚至數千光年以外之地，用來縮短太空探索時間的新科技。但該船在啟動首次的重力跳躍後，便一去不回，直到2047年才重新現身於海王星附近...<br />\n<br />\n3.1914年，來自外星的蒙督沙瓦人到達一座古埃及神廟，取走了四塊石頭和一具石棺，相傳有一種可怕的惡魔每隔5000年就會試圖摧毀宇宙中所有的生命，這四塊石頭分別代表四種元素，石棺中則是第五元素，五種元素相結合可以產生一種光束，是唯一可以抵抗惡魔的武器。2263年，惡魔再度歸來，在太空中的形象仿佛一顆巨大的黑色火球，受到人類戰艦的攻擊後不但沒有被毀，反而更加強大，並通過反擊摧毀了人類戰艦。神父維托&middot;維托科尼利厄斯（Vito Cornelius，伊恩&middot;霍姆飾）是蒙督沙瓦人在地球上的聯絡人，他告訴地球總統（小湯姆&middot;利斯特飾）這種惡魔的來歷，只有五種元素結合才能打敗它。蒙督沙瓦人在前來地球的路上遭孟加羅人僱傭兵伏擊，飛船在地球墜毀，這些孟加羅人是由實業家讓-巴蒂斯特&middot;伊曼紐爾&middot;佐格（Jean-Baptiste Emanuel Zorg，蓋瑞&middot;歐德曼飾）所雇，佐格答應惡魔，為它取得那四塊石頭..<br />\n<br />\n4.故事設定於28世紀的未來，敘述瓦雷諾（丹恩&middot;德翰 飾演）和蘿琳娜（卡拉&middot;迪樂芬妮 飾演）是由人類特派的負責維護整個宇宙秩序的星際旅行特工。瓦雷諾不僅是蘿娜琳的搭檔，還是她的公開追求者。可是由於他的眾多緋聞與女主角傳統價值觀格格不入，導致他的追求之路重挫。受指揮官-艾倫（克萊夫&middot;歐文 飾演）的委派，瓦雷諾和蘿娜琳前往令人心曠神怡的星際城市阿爾法執行一項任務。這是一座欣欣向榮正在不斷擴張的城市，居住來自宇宙各個角落的物種。三千萬的星際居民正在協同努力，積聚他們的智慧和才能讓這個城市變得更加美好..<br />\n<br />\n7 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=iqrmZALveYtknozCzSJN2aS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=8667a56f\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=iqrmZALveYtknozCzSJN2aS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=305edfd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982c2332e7873c645f051afcbf55f721b127ae4c","tid":455709,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac88096709463a78870658a1c62b45bff1da9bf8","tid":455709,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3544ebbc5e86a022440a06acff13c02b65d791fe","tid":455709,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T11:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffdabc6c2a226e4de6539ec715a9378a09c0145","tid":455709,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3938b6e77cbd239a8f1f050978793610f6a2ec06","tid":455709,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T11:54:07.000Z","msg":"算唔算侵權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識法律"},{"pid":"71f1ccd6a402dbb640bb6fe9404d8b3fabbdd3ed","tid":455709,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmo